I'm confused about why the error message talks about TensorFlow 1.4.1.
Perhaps you have conflicting installs for tensorflow and tensorflow-gpu?
Could you try pip list to see what all you have installed and remove all TensorFlow packages and then reinstall?

body:
I'm confused about why the error message talks about TensorFlow 1.4.1.
Perhaps you have conflicting installs for tensorflow and tensorflow-gpu?
Could you try `pip list` to see what all you have installed and remove all TensorFlow packages and then reinstall?
